massbalance

Class EquivalenceClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • massbalance.EquivalenceClass

  • public class EquivalenceClass
extends Object
    Class representing the mass equivalence classes used for mass-balanced randomization.
    Author:
    Georg Basler

      • addAllPairs

        public void addAllPairs(ArrayList<String> names,
               ArrayList<int[]> masses)
        Adds a set of compound pairs and their corresponding mass vectors to the mass equivalence class. Consecutive elements are considered pairs. The sum of the mass vectors of each pair must be linearly dependent on the existing mass vectors of the class.
        Parameters:
        names -
        masses -
